column1: MN State JR/Master Champ & Novice Open
Class   Age     Squat   Bench   Deadlift Total
This year's meet once again proved the strength of powerlifting in Minnesota for both the young and old. We
had a good showing of new lifters as well as veterans in the game. Some records fell in the Master categories
and the competition was tight in many divisions. A solid competition and numbers that lifters can be proud of.
With lifters of this caliber holding their own, next year could prove to be very interesting. I would like to thank
all those involved with making this meet run: judges Ken Andrs, Steve Johnson, Shawn Cain, Brad Madvig,
Maura Shuttleworth - spotters/loaders Josh Pearson, Chris Cooper, Ryan Cooper, Z, Dan Levar, Andrew
Cooper, Randy Abernathy - announcers Randy Bowen, Susan Youngren, Dennis Backscheider, Joe Kilsdonk.
A special thanks goes to my trusty sidekick Bill Omundson who remembers all the parts of a meet that I
forget! If I have forgotten anyone I apologizeâ€¦ thanks again, Joe Cooper
